Detailed Description
Represents the value of a single trial in an experiment.
This class is used to encapsulate and manage data regarding a specific trial, including its unique identifier, state, associated values, and completion date and time. It is intended to facilitate organization and manipulation of trial-related data, often in the context of optimization experiments or similar workflows.
